<P>
   NYC TAXI BOARD LIKELY VIOLATED OPEN MEETINGS LAW, JUDGE SAYS
</P>
<P>
   A8227 BC-SMITH-GLOBE-PROFILE-550&AMP;ADD-NYT 1171 21:55 U A
</P>
<P>
   THE LACK OF TRUTH BRINGS A BOUNTY OF CONSEQUENCES
</P>
<P>
   A8221 BC-OBIT-GIBSON-NYT 373 21:51 U A
</P>
<P>
   (ATTN: Colo.)
</P>
<P>
   A8220 BC-NY-CONSTRUCTION-LICENSING-NYT 1150 21:50 U A
</P>
<P>
