<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-20 09:52 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8556 &Cx1f; var-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-DIANA-DEATH-REVIEW-NY     06-20 0802
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-DIANA-DEATH-REVIEW-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
DI AND DODI: RUMORS AND MONGERS 
</HEADLINE>
   (The Week in Review)  
 (NOTE TO INTERNATIONAL CLIENTS: For international clients' use by
special arrangement only. Asian and European points: contact Karl
Horwitz in Paris for details and prices (Phone: 47 42 17 11; FAX:
47-42-80-44). Latin American points: contact Olivia Vasquez in Los
Angeles (Phone: 310-996-0075; FAX: 310-996-0089) 
(duplication warning: also sent with `i' code) 
(bl)  
 By SARAH LYALL   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service    
